False. Not all mobs have melee damage output that actually requires /disc defensive. Vex Thal mobs, including named do not require warrior tanks. Ssra mobs do not require warrior tanks. Terris Thule, Aedin'Darr, Manaetic Behemoth (maybe, can't recall) can be tanked by hybrids. Hell, at this point, even Avatar of War can probably be tanked by hybrids. This is NOT, as you so claim, a fact. Bertox, Mithaniel, and various other gods require defensive, but the disc isn't law for all tanking<br>
