<br>
Assuming equal tier gear, the pal/sk will be behind anywhere from 500 to about 750 now with pd3? That really isn't alot when your avg buffed warrior in Valor has like 7-8k? Even if you think it's a difference, lemme point out the fact that your avg SK/Pal has like 3k mana... a pair of lifetaps or a single heal (which are chump change to cast with c3) gets rid of that hp gap in any situation where it would be apparent... at the high end, you are looking at 9500hp warriors, and 8500hp + 5000mana paladin/sk's. <br>
